title: Joe Gannascoli from The Sopranos
itunes:title: Joe Gannascoli from The Sopranos
description: This week, Joe Gannascoli from The Sopranos makes an unexpected visit and we talk about cigars that make you go poop. We light up new cigars from Davidoff; Avo Dominant 13, and Davidoff Puro D Oro - Gordito. plus news from the Asylem, American Classic tribute to Bobby Darin and Debonair Cigar and Rum's Gentleman's way.
